    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Interactive Agency Names Top Officers</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Allison Fass</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Fass, Allison</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Martin Reidy, president and chief operating officer of R/GA, an interactive agency, is named to additional post of chief executive (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Executives are changing posts at R/GA in New York, an interactive agency that is part of True North Communications. Martin Reidy, 43, president and chief operating officer, was named to the additional post of chief executive. He succeeds Robert M. Greenberg, 52, chairman, who was named to the additional new post of chief creative officer, overseeing accounts like I.B.M.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Executives are changing posts at R/GA in New York, an interactive agency that is part of True North Communications. Martin Reidy, 43, president and chief operating officer, was named to the additional post of chief executive. He succeeds Robert M. Greenberg, 52, chairman, who was named to the additional new post of chief creative officer, overseeing accounts like I.B.M.</p>
